description: Brock Cooper and I went to a party out in Palm Springs recently. Enjoying the day, also having a few drinks and being in the pool made Brock just want to get naked. With encouragement from me of course, I bring out my camera torecord Brock giving all the guest an unexpected treat. Watch as my super hot surf buddy Brock Cooper gives us all a reason to smile...and jump in a pool!
title: Brock Cooper Poolside, Scene #01
